<p>Welcome!</p>

<p>This blog is built on the premise that finer understanding leads to wiser solutions. I want to raise awareness for ideas and mindsets I believe to be necessary to nudge the world towards a state where we all experience greater fulfillment and peace. At their center lies the notion that dissent, whether inter or intra-individual, is not only unavoidable but necessary. When we let go of our misguided compulsion for homogeneity, we realize that diversity of perspective is a pillar of sustainably harmonious coexistence, rather than an obstacle.</p>

